data.name: btnUnpak.ToolTip
data.value: This button will UnPAK any items checked in the list above (provided they are currently in a PAK file). A dialog will be displayed that will allow you to select the destination for the UnPAK'ed files.

data.name: btnPak.ToolTip
data.value: This button will PAK or RePAK (if there is a current PAK file open) any items checked in the list above. If any items in the original opened PAK file are unchecked, they will be removed from the PAK. The PAK file will be saved at the location specified above the list in the "PAK Save location" box.
